sentence: The  Israel  Defense  Forces  (IDF)  says  it  killed  two  "senior  terror  operatives"  in  a  raid  on  the  Jenin  refugee  camp  in  the  occupied  West  Bank.

article_title: IDF says it killed 'two senior terrorists' in Jenin.
sentence: The  IDF  says  in  a  statement  it  killed  "senior  Palestinian  Islamic  Jihad  operative"  Mohammed  Zubeidi,  and  "local  operative"  Hussam  Hanoun,  Israeli  media  report.
